{"tid":1732913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理行動]  百 萬 人 為 港 發 聲   #推上熱門#","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T04:03:31.000Z","uid":114154,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7fd2c8fe0184ff52805993b67cdadab81c3892","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我而家宣佈發起個人和理行動</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要上街 唔需要犯法</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只係需要你地用兩三分鐘 唱一唱歌 up一up片</span><br />\n我希望616行出來的二百萬人 <br />\n無論你係前線、中學生、銀髮族、爸爸媽媽、返工撚 一齊響應向世界發聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>\\\\\\行動內容///</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今晚<span style=\"color: orange;\">11/18 19:00-24:00</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.</span> <strong>二百萬人一齊錄低自己唱<span style=\"color: green;\">《願榮光歸香港》</span></strong><br />\n戴口罩又好 面具又好 只需要你出把口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. </span><strong>將片UP上<span style=\"color: green;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Twitter</span></em></span></strong><br />\nPO文隨你寫 文章最後加上hashtag <ins>&quot;#GloryToHK&quot;</ins><br />\n<br />\n<em>(就係咁簡單直接 人人都可以參與 唔好再話你無辦法抗爭)</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Q&amp;A</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 又唱歌? 有撚用咩?</strong><br />\nA: <br />\n以前圍爐唱歌只係單純取暖 就算新聞有播 曝光度都極其有限<br />\n今次我地借助社交平台Twitter的力量 務求用壓倒性人數 在短時間內推上世界熱門排名第一爭取各界曝光<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">話比世界知 香港仍然有百萬民意係反對緊政府所做既一切</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 點解用Twitter? 我用慣Facebook喎</strong><br />\nA:<br />\n一、Twitter係國外<strong><ins>最有力</ins></strong>的社交平台 政治人物及平民百姓多數玩Twitter多過玩FB 影響力遍及歐美日韓東南亞<br />\n二、Twitter有<strong><ins>最勁</ins></strong>的搜尋整合功能 無論係搜單字定hashtag 你有PO文就一定會出現在搜尋結果 而FB個搜尋功能只係一pat屎<br />\n三、Twitter行動有<strong><ins>多番實績</ins></strong> 之前<strong>杯葛NBA</strong>/<strong>杯葛暴雪</strong>行動都係老外在Twitter上面發動 <br />\n其行動取得前所未有的成功 最後令NBA同暴雪轉軚<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 一定要今晚搞? 今晚唔得閒可唔可以遲D先搞?</strong><br />\nA:<br />\n中大、理大事件在外界引起核爆 無理由比佢停落來<br />\n而且考慮到香港美國時差 我地19:00正係人地朝早6:00 佢地一起身/嘆緊早餐打開Twitter就聽到香港人的聲音<br />\n依個時間發聲其實係佔盡天時地利<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 我未玩過Twitter 係咪都可以參與?</strong><br />\nA:<br />\n未玩過都歡迎  人人都應該參與<br />\n申請帳號+up片只需要你幾分鐘時間 佢介面同FB差唔多 應該唔影響你up片<br />\n你唔洗在意要follow邊個/入邊個group<br />\n就算你係新ac 淨係為左up一次片 有加hashtag都照樣計數<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q: 有時間唱歌不如出去救手足!</strong><br />\nA:<br />\n我唔反對你咁做 你都係做實事<br />\n但係二百萬手足 想出既人一早出左 剩底既人可能有各式各樣理由同苦衷而唔出得來<br />\n今次行動就係想同呢批人講 <ins>你地仲可以踏出一步  仲有野可以做</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">注意一: </span><br />\n一定要加#GloryToHK <br />\n我地目的係要將呢個tag推上第一 令人一眼望到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">注意二:</span><br />\nTwitter影片有限制 <ins><strong>最長2分20秒</strong></ins><br />\n《願榮光歸香港》已經佔左約2分鐘 <br />\n如果你有其他野想在影片入面講 就得返20秒左右<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">注意三:</span><br />\n未諗到 以下開放自由問答"},{"pid":"7f524f70343c38b8bf40b5e580126d19db269a67","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"766ce3dcd2029a413452a86c001bbb6f1f484917","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"d5b44941deaa356b0323dceb64b078ac6f338a00","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:46:57.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"36e5215ce844ddc464cc6f52960ef9c2af4a6c22","tid":1732913,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9ZjRtg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9ZjRtg.jpg&h=edebd45e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n緊急呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去佐敦啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"bcbe365ac8291d551ec6d0316312e9eb2bf76920","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"bc38978965ff84368ab38372241de0f49003c042","tid":1732913,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6acb2f011cb0e08e669144f884eb53673da71820","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"645042999e2ac578128006745fcfa7d26ae9e6ff","tid":1732913,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"救左poly先"},{"pid":"351d3078c3ded64e7d5d072be375e6ee2ef42350","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"a757d502cbdb99a3b5dfd84d563b21c8d42ca348","tid":1732913,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9397273599deaa9ccfb73198843ab335a2abd43","tid":1732913,"uid":205507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"唱你老母 救咗人先得唔撚得 冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"3a5131eb5727f456123aa8823dd5f8f73fb811cd","tid":1732913,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:48:10.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線最多得幾萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad96f19dbb155adfe88ae0816fe373078c18438","tid":1732913,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy